# Model routing for the content engine. Copy to monitor/.env.local and fill in.
# monitor/.env.local is gitignored — never commit real credentials.
#
# Out of the box (nothing set), the engine uses the default Anthropic client and
# FALLBACK_MODEL. To route bulk generation through a cheaper Anthropic-compatible
# endpoint, set all three BULK_* vars.

# Optional cheap bulk-generation endpoint (any Anthropic-compatible API):
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL="https://your-cheap-endpoint/api/anthropic"
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN="your-token-here"
# BULK_MODEL="your-cheap-model-id"

# Quality fallback used when the bulk endpoint isn't configured or errors:
# FALLBACK_MODEL="claude-opus-4-8"
